---
import Card from "./Card.astro"
---
<section
id="high-quality-software-development"
class="relative bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-950 -top-1 z-10 scroll-mt-16
    px-5 md:px-10 lg:px-20 py-20 md:py-40 items-center"
>
<h1
    class="text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-300 text-center
    font-sans font-light sm:font-normal tracking-tight
    dark:font-extralight dark:sm:font-light
    text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl 2xl:text-7xl 3xl:text-8xl"
>
    <span class="">Plan. Code. Test. Deploy.</span>
</h1>
<h2
    class="font-sans text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400
        text-md sm:text-xl md:text-2xl 2xl:text-3xl text-center max-w-2xl
        mx-auto px-5 md:px-10 py-10 3xl:py-20 mb-5 md:mb-10 lg:mb-20"
>
    Open communication and an iterative development process produce great results.
</h2>
<ul role="list" class="grid mx-auto space-y-6 md:grid-cols-2 md:space-y-0 justify-center">
    <Card
        href="https://docs.astro.build/"
        title="Documentation"
        body="Learn how Astro works and explore the official API docs."
    />
    <Card
        href="https://astro.build/integrations/"
        title="Integrations"
        body="Supercharge your project with new frameworks and libraries."
    />
    <Card
        href="https://astro.build/themes/"
        title="Themes"
        body="Explore a galaxy of community-built starter themes."
    />
    <Card
        href="https://astro.build/chat/"
        title="Community"
        body="Come say hi to our amazing Discord community. ❤️"
    />
</ul>
</section>